Last week, I did a Zoom reading for a woman and a young man. 

🕊️ The reading began with the woman’s mother in spirit, who stepped forward first in the reading. Then the woman’s brother in spirit. Both spirits brought through some healing messages.

✨ Then, I felt the energy shift within minutes into the reading. The two energies in spirit, were now bringing through a younger male in spirit.

👦🏼 As this young man’s gentle spirit moves closer to me—I now begin to realize this is the woman’s son in spirit and the son’s father. 

⚡️ I immediately can feel so many mix emotions not only from the clients, but as well from her son in spirit. 

❤️ The woman’s son wanted to express how much he appreciated his mother for helping him on his health journey, as well for continuing taking care of his kids after his passed.

😀 More importantly, he wanted to tell his mom and son’s that he was still able to keep his sense of humor in the after life.

➡️ During the reading, the woman’s son was joking around about his funeral services and how he did NOT want it the same, how most people do their services. He was telling me, that there is a funny story about it and he wants to make sure that they follow through with it.

🗣️ The father’s son tells me, “My dad said, when he passes away, he wants his funeral services to be Viking themed related.” We all laughed. 🤣

💙 It is these little validation/ messages in a reading that can make a big difference letting the family know that the soul still survives after death. 

😞 Reason, why? Her son’s funeral & burial has not even taken place yet. Her son will be laid to rest next week. 😳

🔮 I recently did a virtual reading for a gentleman. As Psychic Medium, I know that every client that I speak with has that special person that he or she absolutely wants to connect with in the afterlife. 

👼🏼 During my virtual reading with this man, I immediately recognize a younger male in spirit stepping forward. This young man’s energy felt very strong and personal .

😁 I began to describing this young male’s personality, how he passed, what he looked like here in the physical world, hobbies and more.

😲 The man receiving the messages, paused and got emotional. “This is my son that you are connecting with. By what you just said, describes him to a tee.”

🤨 As a psychic medium, I always give what I get from spirit. Even if the reference seems so left field.

🔋 “Your son is telling to tell you about the alarm and that it is not the batteries. Does that makes sense?” I asked, figuring he would say, no.

🪫 The man gasps and says, “Holy Sh**! You have to be kidding me!” He put his hand over his mouth, little shocked. He continues to validate, “For little over a week now, my smoke detector in my house and my car alarm keeps going off. I have changed out the batteries in my smoke detector twice now. I even changed my car battery too! I can’t believe you just said that!”

🤭 I started laughing, as I am seeing this as a confirmation from his son in spirit letting his father know that he is doing absolutely fine.

🪧 Sometimes, we may receive messages from our passed loved ones as being very subtle or in big extravagant ways. Don’t look for the signs. They will happen organically.

❤️ Remember, love never dies.

“My son, was an amazing young man. He had everything going for him. A supportive family, great job, financial well, he didn’t drink or do drugs.  I was lost. I wanted answers. Why did my son leave us? I took an unorthodox path. I begin speaking with Mediums hoping my son would provide me with answers. Many of the Mediums provided information that was generic. Few provided very insightful information, which help me tremendously.  Fast forward, a couple years have passed since my son has gained his wings. A girlfriend of mine gave me a call and said, ‘I have an extra ticket to go see a Medium. Are you interested going?’ I said, “Sure.”  I wasn’t expecting to receive a message while sitting in the audience. But then, a magical moment happened. A.J. begins, getting a feeling towards the back of the room of a son energy, where his actions caused his passing. I raised my hand & stood up.  A.J. said, “Would you understand his passing being a high to low passing, like someone falling, aircraft, jumping, etc.”  I said, “My son made a gut-wrenching decision and leap off a bridge to his death.” At this point, you could hear a pin drop in the room.  A.J. continues, “I am going to be honestly. I’m not getting a lot of information from your son. But he is saying, ‘Please tell my mom to stop searching. It is not your fault. You couldn’t have saved me. I will always be with you and love you always.’”  I left A.J.’s event in tears of happiness. That evening on, my healing journey truly began. I stopped blaming myself. Not to mention, my son and I would always say to each other, ‘love you always.’ That is all the validation I needed. ⬇️

During a recent zoom reading, I connected a mother with her son in the spirit realm. 😢

Those who are familiar with my work, either experiencing a personal private reading, live audience event, online group reading event or a social media live,… I always give what I get from spirit.

😇 When spirit shows me something twice in a reading, I know there is an important meaning to why spirit is showing me a symbol/ reference. Even if it doesn’t make complete sense to me as a Medium, typically it will makes sense to the client.

In the beginning of this woman’s reading, her son in spirit kept showing me a chicken. Yes, a chicken! 🐥 The first time around, when I was saw the impression, I didn’t connect with it nor did I bring it up because there wasn’t meaning to me.

15-20 minutes into her 30 minute reading, I was shown a chicken again. 😆 At this point, I let the mother know, “Your son is showing me a chicken. He has shown it to me twice now. I have absolute no meaning for it. Why would he show me a chicken?”

The mother begins to laugh and says, “Wow.” She then takes a short pause and continues to say, “I use to tell my son, he is my chicken little. He even wore those round glasses, like in the movie.” 🥹

I always try to express to audiences & clients that a Medium has no control who or what will come through in a reading. 

People have high expectations in a reading, which is understandable. Majority of people always want to hear that ONE specific ‘thing’ to make the reading valid. 

Just because that one thing does not come through in a reading, doesn’t mean that your loved one in spirit loves you any less. The messages that your loved one in spirit bring forth in a reading is what YOU need to hear. ❤️

📖 Quick story... 👀

During a client’s reading that was conducted this morning, one of her loved ones in spirit was showing me something very unusual. I didn’t really have a meaning for it.

I asked her, “Is there some weird reason why he is showing me a fly 🪰 or some sort of insect?”

She smiled and said, “I know what it is. It’s a bee. 🐝 When I see a bee land on my car or in my car, I connect it to that specific loved one.” 💕

I then say to her, “Wow. That is super cool. Out of the years of driving my vehicle, I have never notice a bee on my car.” 🤷🏽‍♂️

🕰️ Fast forward a few hours later. I was getting into my car. I put on my seat belt and I just so happen to look at the top of my windshield and I see a bee! 🐝😱

I took a moment and I laughed. The bee began moving directly in front of me on the window. I grabbed my phone and took this photo. 🤳

Spirit has a funny way of showing even the Medium a “sign” or even their humor from beyond. 🪽

Kudos to Spirit. 💙
